                <ptr target="../persons/pers2091">Mrs Wesley</ptr>
            </persName>
         <seg ana="money">Twenty pounds</seg> on Acc. of Paying for the <seg ana="publishing">press</seg>. Materials etc., by <persName>
                <ptr target="../persons/pers0072">Will
               Atkinson</ptr>
            </persName>.' There follows in a different hand a list of
         accounted items.</p>
